2d","tid":699791,"uid":104443,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T21:52:04.000Z","msg":"唔好咁輕易就話去死，你一時嘅痛苦，你家人朋友就一世嘅痛苦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T21:53:43.000Z","msg":"啱呀 頂下頂下就一千歲"},{"pid":"6b88672ba7b823d01d66deb5ac38e8edbc4fff3d","tid":699791,"uid":104443,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T21:54:04.000Z","msg":"我琴日寫好篇勸世文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宜家就拎出嚟比你睇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/123519_a36ab141fed0d969dfca46316d7cf4da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F123519_a36ab141fed0d969dfca46316d7cf4da.png&h=fe75b758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果投着個咁豬扒嘅八婆你仲會唔會想死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而且幅圖未講仲有<br />\n1/5機會投做非洲班黑人<br />\n1/5機會投做姦國印度人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲未計中東班伊斯蘭、南美原始部落呢咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 保守估計至少70%都會投咗去地獄鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果仲要投着女人就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘅然今生「比較」有幸做到香港人，點解大家唔去珍惜，要去玩埋曬呢啲輸多贏少嘅投胎遊戲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8399eb5b907d187a9bf96b78dbe5a13ddfab8e8","tid":699791,"uid":138860,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T21:57:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b089ed5760608e4f4802632ea1dc35e188a50111","tid":699791,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T21:59:09.000Z","msg":"係囉，究竟發生咩